    "name": "Rat Climber",
    "steam_appid": 3085180,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You are a rat. You must climb. </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reach the top, claim the cheese! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Rat Climber, you only have one goal: reach the top of the world.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must navigate vertical labyrinths and make daring jumps, but be careful; one false move and you go tumbling down.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>No Collectibles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Just climb and explore! But there may be a secret cheese in each zone, and something special might happen upon finding them all... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Every object has exact collision</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- If there's a small hole, you can probably fit inside. A 3 inch ledge? You can stand on it, Ratty! Start thinking like a <i>rat.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>There are no power ups or skills</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- There are <i>only</i> 3 controls: Jump, dash, and walk </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dash lets you jump farther and <i>slightly higher</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085180/extras/cdfe6a9eb5ee661af50f6ace0704ce2a.poster.avif?t=1756391307\" width=366 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085180/extras/cdfe6a9eb5ee661af50f6ace0704ce2a.webm?t=1756391307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085180/extras/cdfe6a9eb5ee661af50f6ace0704ce2a.mp4?t=1756391307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The walk allows for precise movement and <i>prevents you from walking off of ledges</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085180/extras/bf02a83854bef6471f0a37498e45995a.poster.avif?t=1756391307\" width=368 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085180/extras/bf02a83854bef6471f0a37498e45995a.webm?t=1756391307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085180/extras/bf02a83854bef6471f0a37498e45995a.mp4?t=1756391307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you fall, there's a chance you could recover progress from a recovery path, or land in a previous zone below you, but it's not guaranteed!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you guide Ratty to the top of the world and reach cheese heaven? Try your skills in the best 3D ratformer ever made! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DEFAULT CONTROLS (run and walk keybindings can be changed in the options menu) </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keyboard Controls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shift:</strong> Run</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Left Ctrl:</strong> Safety Walk (will not walk off of ledges as long as held down)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Spacebar:</strong> Jump</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enter/Esc/Backspace:</strong> Options Menu</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>E:</strong> Interact</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>T:</strong> First Person Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Xbox Controller Controls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>B Button:</strong> Run</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>X Button:</strong> Safety Walk (will not walk off of ledges as long as held down)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Button:</strong> Jump</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Start/Options Button:</strong> Options Menu</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Right Trigger:</strong> Interact</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>L3:</strong> Camera Reset</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>R3:</strong> First Person Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Start Button:</strong> Options Menu</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>L3:</strong> Re-center camera</p>",
